In addition to the quantities laid down in Commission Regulation (EC) No 1545/2007, a complementary quantity of 120 000 tonnes of complementary raw cane sugar in white sugar equivalent is fixed for the marketing year 2007/2008:
(a) 116 000 tonnes expressed as white sugar originating in the States listed in Annex VI to Regulation (EC) No 318/2006 except India;
(b) 4 000 tonnes expressed as white sugar originating in India.
